# ShieldAction.primaryButtonPressed

**Case**

The user pressed the top button of the buttons on a shield.

## Declaration

```swift
case primaryButtonPressed
```

## Buttons

- **ShieldAction.secondaryButtonPressed**: The user pressed the optional secondary button underneath the primary button of a shield.
